comments.body: @maropu . Since you are merging ParquetReadBenchmark and OrcReadBenchmark benchmarks, let's remove [OrcReadBenchmark](https://github.com/apache/spark/blob/master/sql/hive/src/test/scala/org/apache/spark/sql/hive/orc/OrcReadBenchmark.scala).
I feel we still need to `OrcReadBenchmark` to compare native `orc` with `Hive built-in orc`?
I see. Never mind. I deleted the previous comment. The scope is only testing `native orc` here.
